<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Login Verification - <%= companyName %></title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #28a745 0%, #20c997 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        
        .header p {
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        
        .greeting {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #333;
        }
        
        .message {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }
        
        .login-info {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-left: 4px solid #28a745;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
        }
        
        .login-details {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .login-details strong {
            color: #28a745;
        }
        
        .otp-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 40px 0;
        }
        
        .otp-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e8f5e8 0%, #d4edda 100%);
            border: 2px dashed #28a745;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 30px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .otp-code {
            font-size: 42px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #28a745;
            letter-spacing: 12px;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        
        .otp-label {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #888;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        
        .security-alert {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff3cd 0%, #ffeaa7 100%);
            border: 1px solid #ffc107;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }
        
        .alert-icon {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-right: 15px;
            margin-top: 2px;
        }
        
        .alert-content {
            flex: 1;
        }
        
        .alert-content h3 {
            color: #856404;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .alert-content p {
            color: #856404;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        
        .not-you-section {
            background: #f8d7da;
            border: 1px solid #f5c6cb;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .not-you-section h3 {
            color: #721c24;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .not-you-section p {
            color: #721c24;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .security-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background: #dc3545;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .footer {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .footer a {
            color: #28a745;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        .footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        
        .device-info {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #999;
            margin-top: 15px;
            padding: 10px;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .email-container {
                margin: 10px;
                border-radius: 5px;
            }
            
            .header, .content, .footer {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            
            .otp-code {
                font-size: 32px;
                letter-spacing: 8px;
            }
            
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
            
            .login-details {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>🔐 Login Verification</h1>
            <p>Secure access to your account</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">
                Hello <%= fullname %>! 👤
            </div>
            
            <div class="message">
                We received a login request for your <%= companyName %> account. To ensure the security of your account, 
                please verify this login attempt using the verification code below.
            </div>
            
            <div class="login-info">
                <h3 style="color: #28a745; margin-bottom: 15px;">📋 Login Attempt Details:</h3>
                <div class="login-details">
                    <span><strong>Email:</strong> <%= email %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="login-details">
                    <span><strong>Time:</strong> <%= new Date().toLocaleString() %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="login-details">
                    <span><strong>Request Type:</strong> OTP Login</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="otp-section">
                <div class="otp-label">Your Login Verification Code</div>
                <div class="otp-box">
                    <div class="otp-code"><%= otp %></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="security-alert">
                <div class="alert-icon">🛡️</div>
                <div class="alert-content">
                    <h3>Security Information</h3>
                    <p><strong>Expires in:</strong> <%= expirationTime %> minutes</p>
                    <p><strong>Valid for:</strong> One-time use only</p>
                    <p><strong>Keep secure:</strong> Never share this code with anyone</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="not-you-section">
                <h3>🚨 Wasn't you trying to log in?</h3>
                <p>If you didn't request this login code, your account may be at risk.</p>
                <a href="mailto:<%= supportEmail %>?subject=Suspicious Login Activity" class="security-btn">
                    Report Suspicious Activity
                </a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="message">
                <strong>Important:</strong> Enter this code only on the official <%= companyName %> website. 
                Our team will never ask for your verification code via phone, email, or any other method.
            </div>
            
            <div class="device-info">
                <strong>Security Tip:</strong> Always verify the URL in your browser before entering any codes. 
                Look for the secure lock icon and ensure you're on the correct domain.
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Need assistance? Contact our security team at <a href="mailto:<%= supportEmail %>"><%= supportEmail %></a></p>
            <p>This verification code was sent to <strong><%= email %></strong></p>
            <p>&copy; <%= currentYear %> <%= companyName %>. All rights reserved.</p>
            
            <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #999;">
                This is an automated security email. Please do not reply to this message.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>